p (song)|Teardrop]]\" \n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| style=\"background:#FFC40C;text-align:center;\" | '''{{green|\u2714}}'''\n|-\n!  Khadija\n| 4\n| 21\n| \"[[Underwater Love (Smoke City song)|Underwater Love]]\"\n| style=\"background:#FFC40C;text-align:center;\" | '''{{green|\u2714}}'''\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n|-style=\"background:#DCDCDC;\"\n! Craig Roystone\n| 5\n| 21\n| \"[[This Is The Last Time]]\"\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n|-\n! Nikki Ambers\n| 6\n| 22\n| \"[[Better Now (Post Malone song)|Better Now]]\"\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| '''{{green|\u2714}}''' \n| style=\"background:#fdfc8f;|'''{{green|\u2714}}'''\n|-\n! Seth Oraeki\n| 7\n| 17\n| \"[[Jealous (Labrinth song)|Jealous]]\"\n| style=\"background:#fdfc8f;|'''{{green|\u2714}}'''\n| '''{{green|\u2714}}''' \n|\u2014\n|\u2014\n|-\n! Moya\n| style=\"background-color:#B2EC5D;\" | 8\n| style=\"background-color:#B2EC5D;\" | 27\n| style=\"background-color:#B2EC5D;\" | \"[[Human (Rag'n'Bone Man album)|Grace]]\"\n| '''{{green|\u2714}}'''\n| style=\"background:#fdfc8f;|'''{{green|\u2714}}'''\n| '''{{green|\u2714}}'''\n| '''{{green|\u2714}}'''\n|}\n\n=== Episode 6 (9 February) ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center; width:100%;\"\n! rowspan=\"2\" scope=\"col\" style=\"width:13%;\" |Artist\n! rowspan=\"2\" scope=\"col\" style=\"width:05%;\" |Order\n! rowspan=\"2\" scope=\"col\" style=\"width:05%;\" |Age\n! rowspan=\"2\" scope=\"col\" style=\"width:26%;\" |Song\n! colspan=\"4\" style=\"width:40%;\" |Coaches and artists choices\n|-\n! style=\"width:10%;\" |[[will.i.am]]\n! style=\"width:10%;\" |[[Jennifer Hudson|Jennifer]]\n! style=\"width:10%;\" |[[Tom Jones (singer)|Tom]]\n! style=\"width:10%;\" |[[Olly Murs|Olly]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | Nyema Kalfon\n| 1\n| 22\n| \"[[Answerphone (Banx & Ranx and Ella Eyre song)|Answerphone]]\"\n| style=\"background:#fdfc8f;| '''{{green|\u2714}}'''\n| \u2014\n| '''{{green|\u2714}}'''\n| \u2014\n|-\n! Gabriel Dryss\n| 2\n| 16\n| \"[[Treasure (Bruno Mars song)|Treasure]]\"\n| style=\"background:#FFC40C;text-align:center;\" | '''{{green|\u2714}}'''\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n|-style=\"background:#DCDCDC;\"\n! Clare McCulloch\n| 3\n| 34\n| \"[[Hard to Handle (song)|Hard to Handle]]\"\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n|-\n! Gisela Green\n| 4\n| 27\n| \"[[Freudian (album)|Best Part]]\"\n| '''{{green|\u2714}}'''\n| style=\"background:#fdfc8f;|'''{{green|\u2714}}'''\n| \u2014\n| '''{{green|\u2714}}'''\n|-style=\"background:#DCDCDC;\"\n! Stephanie Hill\n| 5\n| 24\n| \"[[I Could Have Danced All Night]]\"\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n|-\n! [[Georgia Bray]]\n|6\n| 21\n| \"[[Firework (song)|Firework]]\"\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| style=\"background:#FFC40C;text-align:center;\" | '''{{green|\u2714}}'''\n|-style=\"background:#DCDCDC;\"\n! Jack Hawitt\n|7\n| 29\n| \"[[Diamonds (Rihanna song)|Diamonds]]\"\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n|-style=\"background:#DCDCDC;\"\n! Kenza Blanka\n|8\n| 34\n| \"[[Papaoutai]]\"\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n|-\n! Deana Walmsley\n|9\n| 23\n| \"[[Back to Black (song)|Back to Black]]\"\n| '''{{green|\u2714}}'''\n| \u2014\n| style=\"background:#fdfc8f;|'''{{green|\u2714}}'''\n| '''{{green|\u2714}}'''\n|}\n\n=== Episode 7 (16 February) ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center; width:100%;\"\n! rowspan=\"2\" scope=\"col\" style=\"width:13%;\" |Artist\n! rowspan=\"2\" scope=\"col\" style=\"width:05%;\" |Order\n! rowspan=\"2\" scope=\"col\" style=\"width:05%;\" |Age\n! rowspan=\"2\" scope=\"col\" style=\"width:26%;\" |Song\n! colspan=\"4\" style=\"width:40%;\" |Coaches and artists choices\n|-\n! style=\"width:10%;\" |[[will.i.am]]\n! style=\"width:10%;\" |[[Jennifer Hudson|Jennifer]]\n! style=\"width:10%;\" |[[Tom Jones (singer)|Tom]]\n! style=\"width:10%;\" |[[Olly Murs|Olly]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | Shivon Kane\n| 1\n| 19\n| \"[[Fine Line (Mabel song)|Fine Line]]\"\n| style=\"background:#FFC40C;text-align:center;\" | '''{{green|\u2714}}''