oice introduces new lifeline vote\n|website=BT|language=en|access-date=2019-03-30}}</ref>\n\n===Episode 1 (16 March)===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center; width:65%;\"\n|-\n! Order\n! Coach\n! Artist\n! Song\n! Result\n|-\n! 1\n| rowspan=3| Sir Tom Jones\n| Deana Walmsley\n| \"[[Dusk Till Dawn (Zayn song)|Dusk Till Dawn]]\"\n| style=\"background:lightgreen;\" | Advanced\n|-\n! 2\n| style=\"background:pink;\" | Roger Samuels\n| style=\"background:pink;\" | \"[[Grace (Lewis Capaldi song)|Grace]]\"\n| rowspan=\"3\" style=\"background:pink;\" | Eliminated\n|-\n! 3\n| style=\"background:pink;\" | Equip to Overcome\n| style=\"background:pink;\" | \"[[When Love Takes Over]]\"\n|-\n! 1\n| rowspan=3| Jennifer Hudson\n| style=\"background:pink;\" | Connie Lamb\n| style=\"background:pink;\" | \"[[2002 (song)|2002]]\" \n|-\n! 2\n| Moya\n| \"[[Woman (Neneh Cherry song)|Woman]]\"\n| style=\"background:lightgreen;\" | Advanced\n|-\n! 3\n| style=\"background:pink;\" | Sarah Tucker\n| style=\"background:pink;\" | \"[[The Edge of Glory]]\"\n| style=\"background:pink;\" | Eliminated\n|-\n! 1\n| rowspan=3| will.i.am\n| NXTGEN\n| \"[[Runnin' (Lose It All)]]\"\n| style=\"background:lightgreen;\" | Advanced\n|-\n! 2\n| style=\"background:pink;\" | Callum Butterworth\n| style=\"background:pink;\" | \"[[Mirrors (Justin Timberlake song)|Mirrors]]\"\n| rowspan=\"4\" style=\"background:pink;\" | Eliminated\n|-\n! 3\n| style=\"background:pink;\" | Gabriel Dryss\n| style=\"background:pink;\" | \"[[Just Got Paid (Sigala song)|Just Got Paid]]\"\n|-\n! 1\n| rowspan=3| Olly Murs\n| style=\"background:pink;\" | Eva Campbell\n| style=\"background:pink;\" | \"[[Unstoppable (Sia song)|Unstoppable]]\" \n|-\n! 2\n| style=\"background:pink;\" | Harrisen Larner-Main\n| style=\"background:pink;\" | \"[[You Get What You Give (song)|You Get What You Give]]\"\n|-\n! 3\n| Jimmy Balito\n| \"[[High and Dry]]\"\n| style=\"background:lightgreen;\" | Advanced\n|-\n|}\n\n===Episode 2 (23 March)===\n{|