work)|ITV]] that the eighth series would begin broadcasting on 5 January 2019.<ref>{{cite news|author1=ITV|authorlink1=ITV (TV network)|title=''The Voice'' returns in January!|url=http://www.itv.com/thevoice/the-voice-returns-in-january|accessdate=18 December 2017|work=[[ITV plc]]|date=4 December 2017|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171218193523/http://www.itv.com/thevoice/the-voice-returns-in-january|archivedate=18 December 2017|location=United Kingdom}}</ref>\n\n;Colour key\n{| class=\"toccolours\" style=\"font-size: 90%; white-space: nowrap;\"\n|-\n| style=\"background-color:white; border: 1px solid black;\" | &nbsp;'''{{green|\u2714}}'''&nbsp;\n| Coach hit his/her \"I WANT YOU\" button<!---[[File:Red button.png|15px]][ [File:Crystal Clear app clean.png|15px]] '''{{green|{{unicode|\u2714}}}}'''!--->\n|-\n| style=\"background-color:#FFC40C; border: 1px solid black\" | &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n| Artist defaulted to this coach's team\n|-\n| style=\"background-color:#fdfc8f; border: 1px solid black;\" | &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n| style=\"padding-right: 8px\" | Artist elected to join this coach's team\n|-\n| style=\"background-color:#DCDCDC; border: 1px solid black\" | &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n| Artist eliminated with no coach pressing his or her \"I WANT YOU\" button\n|-\n| style=\"background-color:#B2EC5D; border: 1px solid black\" | &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n| Artist Received an \"All Turn\"\n|-\n\n|-\n|}\n\n=== Episode 1 (5 January) ===\nThe series premiere aired on from 8:30pm until 9:35pm.\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center; width:100%;\"\n! rowspan=\"2\" scope=\"col\" style=\"width:13%;\" |Artist\n! rowspan=\"2\" scope=\"col\" style=\"width:05%;\" |Order\n! rowspan=\"2\" scope=\"col\" style=\"width:05%;\" |Age\n! rowspan=\"2\" scope=\"col\" style=\"width:26%;\" |Song\n! colspan=\"4\" style=\"width:40%;\" |Coaches and artists choices\n|-\n! style=\"width:10%;\" |[[will.i.am]]\n! style=\"width:10%;\" |[[Jennifer Hudson|Jennifer]]\n! s